<p>Batumi International University (BIU) is a private university located in Batumi, Georgia. The university was established in 2009 and has since become one of the most popular destinations for international students seeking higher education in Georgia. With a focus on internationalization, modern teaching methods, and a commitment to research and innovation, BIU has gained a reputation as a leading institution of higher education in the region.</p>
