 <h3>Admission and Tuition Fees:</h3>
 <p>BIU has a straightforward admission process for international students. Prospective students can apply online or through an authorized representative. The university requires certain documents, including academic transcripts, language proficiency tests, and a statement of purpose.</p>

<p>Tuition fees at BIU are relatively affordable compared to other universities in Europe or North America. The university also offers scholarships and financial aid to deserving students.</p>
